      h3 LFSP Workshop: Scientists, Politics and how thinking in tanks can help
      p
        |When: 6pm-8pm 28th January 2014
        |Where: South Kensington Campus, Roderic Hill Building, Aero Level 2, Lecture Theatre 266
        |How Much: Free!
        |There’s no experience of politics necessary at all and it’ll be a friendly introductory session to explain what a think tank is, how it works and what we do.
        |It’s an active session and we’ll equip you with the tools you need to get involved in politics and start bringing your scientific expertise to the world of government.
